reviews.review_text: Joan Baez~ Revenge of Donna! Hee-hee, that's right! She must've been in communication with ol' Donna. Actually she sounds a bit like Marty Balin, just singin' up a storm. Actually she does sound just fine to me. Did you know ol' Joanie did a Christmas album back in 1966? I't the best x-mas album ever!
